comment: Existence form of ~ infxpenc . A "uniform" or "canonical" version of ~ infxpen , asserting the existence of a single function ` g ` that simultaneously demonstrates product idempotence of all ordinals below a given bound. (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 30-May-2015.)
